msItem.rubric:
Nomina sacra; names of the donor; name of the protagonist (the name Libanos; the name Mäṭaˤ is not rubricated);
elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numbers.
Four lines, divided into two groups alternating with black lines, in the incipit folio of Text 1 (fol. 3rab);
incipit of some subsections (one or two lines) in Text I; incipit of Text II (fol. 47r); incipit of each miracle (fols. 56ra, l.14, 57ra, l.12); the word sälam.

